{"text_id":258313,"tokens":["Phylogenetic"," diversity",","," a"," critical"," component"," of"," ecosystem"," resilience",","," is"," increasingly"," threatened"," by"," species"," ext","inctions","."," To"," mitigate"," this"," loss",","," conservation"," efforts"," often"," focus"," on"," preserving"," a"," representative"," subset"," of"," species",","," yet"," the"," expected"," contribution"," of"," each"," species"," to"," future"," phylogenetic"," diversity"," remains"," poorly"," understood","."," We"," addressed"," this"," knowledge"," gap"," by"," predicting"," the"," expected"," contribution"," of"," species"," to"," future"," phylogenetic"," diversity"," under"," different"," conservation"," scenarios","."," We"," used"," a"," Monte"," Carlo"," simulation"," approach"," to"," model"," the"," fate"," of"," species"," under"," various"," habitat"," loss"," and"," fragmentation"," scenarios",","," and"," subsequently"," calculated"," the"," expected"," phylogenetic"," diversity"," at"," different"," times","cales","."," Our"," results"," indicate"," that"," a"," small"," subset"," of"," highly"," threatened"," and"," ecologically"," distinct"," species"," contributes"," disproportion","ately"," to"," future"," phylogenetic"," diversity",","," suggesting"," that"," conservation"," efforts"," should"," prioritize"," these"," species","."," We"," also"," found"," that"," the"," timing"," and"," magnitude"," of"," conservation"," actions"," can"," significantly"," affect"," the"," long","-","term"," persistence"," of"," phylogenetic"," diversity","."," Our"," work"," highlights"," the"," importance"," of"," considering"," the"," expected"," contribution"," of"," species"," to"," future"," phylogenetic"," diversity"," when"," designing"," conservation"," strategies",","," and"," provides"," a"," framework"," for"," conservation","ists"," to"," identify"," the"," most"," effective"," and"," efficient"," conservation"," efforts","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"llama3-8b","label":1}